<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Get Global Yields"
  description="Learn about the dedicated team behind Get Global Yields."
>
  <div class="bg-primary-900 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg prose-a:text-accent-500 hover:prose-a:text-accent-400 max-w-none">
        <h1>About GetGlobalYields</h1>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Meet the Author</h2>

        <p><strong>Tzion S.</strong><br>
        Founder &amp; Editor, GetGlobalYields</p>

        <p>Hi, I'm Tzion — the person behind GetGlobalYields.</p>

        <p>I hold a Bachelor's degree in Economics and Management, and I've spent years working at the intersection of finance and data. For five years, I worked at a company building financial information software for the Tel Aviv Stock Exchange, where I specialized in bond data — taking raw fixed-income data straight from the exchange, processing it, and integrating it into systems that financial clients relied on daily. That work gave me a close, hands-on understanding of how market data actually moves from source to decision-maker.</p>

        <p>Alongside that, I've been personally investing in the Israeli stock market for years, and for the past 4.5 years I've been actively investing in the US stock market as well — navigating exactly the kind of cross-border challenges (tax treaties, reporting, account structures) that this site is built to help you with.</p>

        <p>I started GetGlobalYields because I saw how much confusing, US-centric, or outdated information non-US investors have to wade through just to invest confidently in American markets. My goal is to turn what I've learned — both from working with financial data professionally and from investing my own money across two markets — into clear, practical guides.</p>

        <h3 class="text-slate-100">Background</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Education:</strong> B.A. in Economics and Management</li>
          <li><strong>Professional experience:</strong> 5 years processing and integrating Tel Aviv Stock Exchange bond/fixed-income data for a financial software company</li>
          <li><strong>Investing experience:</strong> Active investor in the Israeli stock market (multi-year) and the US stock market (4.5+ years)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-slate-100">How this content is created</h3>
        <p>Articles on GetGlobalYields are researched and written based on primary sources — including tax treaties, IRS/brokerage documentation, and exchange data — and reviewed for accuracy before publishing. Where AI tools assist in drafting, all content is fact-checked and edited by me personally before it goes live. This site does not provide personalized financial or tax advice; always consult a licensed advisor for decisions specific to your situation.</p>

        <h3 class="text-slate-100">Contact</h3>
        <p>Have a question or feedback? Feel free to <a href="/contact/">reach out</a>.</p>

        <hr>

        <p><em>Last reviewed: July 7, 2026</em></p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
